Roblox Name: TheRealFoltyn

Insta: https://www.instagram.com/realfoltyn/

Twitter: https://twitter.com/Foltynnn

What is Roblox? ROBLOX is an online virtual playground and workshop, where kids of all ages can safely interact, create, have fun, and learn. It’s unique in that practically everything on ROBLOX is designed and constructed by members of the community. ROBLOX is designed for 13 to 18 year olds, but it is open to people of all ages. Each player starts by choosing an avatar and giving it an identity. They can then explore ROBLOX — interacting with others by chatting, playing games, or collaborating on creative projects. Each player is also given their own piece of undeveloped real estate along with a virtual toolbox with which to design and build anything — be it a navigable skyscraper, a working helicopter, a giant pinball machine, a multiplayer “Capture the Flag” game or some other, yet-to-be-dreamed-up creation. There is no cost for this first plot of virtual land. By participating and by building cool stuff, ROBLOX members can earn specialty badges as well as ROBLOX dollars (“Robux”). In turn, they can shop the online catalog to purchase avatar clothing and accessories as well as premium building materials, interactive components, and working mechanisms.

It’s unique in that practically everything on ROBLOX is designed and constructed by members of the community. ROBLOX is designed for 13 to 18 year olds, but it is open to people of all ages. Each player starts by choosing an avatar and giving it an identity. They can then explore ROBLOX — interacting with others by chatting, playing games, or collaborating on creative projects. Each player is also given their own piece of undeveloped real estate along with a virtual toolbox with which to design and build anything — be it a navigable skyscraper, a working helicopter, a giant pinball machine, a multiplayer “Capture the Flag” game or some other, yet-to-be-dreamed-up creation. snippet.title: Terminator 7: Final War (2025) - First Trailer | Arnold Schwarzenegger
snippet.description:
#terminator #terminator7finalwar #arnoldschwarzenegger 

Schwarzenegger leads humanity in Terminator’s final chapter. 

Editing, VFX, SFX, Thumbnail by @KHStudio please subscribe:
✅ YouTube: https://bit.ly/KHstudio

🎥 Attention viewers!

Please note that this video is a concept trailer created solely for artistic and entertainment purposes. I have meticulously incorporated various effects, sound design, AI technologies (Google Veo 3), movie analytics, and other elements to bring my vision to life. Its purpose is purely artistic, aiming to entertain and engage with the YouTube community. My goal is to showcase my creativity and storytelling skills through this trailer. Thank you for your support, and let's dive into the world of imagination! 🍿

🤖  Terminator 7: Final War

Speculation is mounting that Terminator 7: Final War may be in development, with Arnold Schwarzenegger rumored to reprise his legendary role one final time. The project is said to bring the decades-long battle between humanity and Skynet to a dramatic conclusion, closing the chapter on one of science fiction’s most iconic franchises. Schwarzenegger’s possible return has generated widespread attention, with many believing this could serve as both a farewell to the character and a definitive finale to the series.

Whispers about the story suggest that Final War will take place in a timeline where the resistance has gained significant ground, setting up a climactic confrontation between man and machine. Rumors indicate that the film will emphasize large-scale battles, integrating futuristic technology with grounded character drama, and that it may include flashbacks showing earlier phases of the war. The sense of closure could allow the franchise to finally tie together its complex timelines.

The rumored tone of Final War is said to be darker and more apocalyptic than recent entries, leaning into the despair of humanity’s last stand while celebrating resilience and sacrifice. Fans are speculating that the film will not only showcase massive war sequences but also offer an emotional farewell to Schwarzenegger’s T-800, bringing his journey full circle. If true, this project could mark the definitive end of one of cinema’s longest-running sagas.

Feel free to express your thoughts on this exciting project by leaving a comment below.

snippet.title: BOOTS | Official Trailer | Netflix
snippet.description:
It’s 1990, you’re fresh out of high school and not sure what to do with your life, so, obviously, you follow your buddy blindly into the US Marine Corps... What could go wrong? Inspired by a real manly story, BOOTS marches onto Netflix October 9.

Song: "Freedom! '90" by #GeorgeMichael covered by the San Diego Gay Men's Chorus

Add this to your watch list: https://www.netflix.com/BOOTS That’s a direct order!

BOOTS is a one-hour comedic drama that delivers an irreverent, off-beat take on the coming-of-age story. Set in the tough, unpredictable world of the 1990s US Marine Corps—when being gay in the military was still illegal—the series follows directionless, closeted Cameron Cope (#MilesHeizer) and his best friend Ray McAffey (Liam Oh), the son of a decorated Marine, as they join a diverse group of recruits. Together, this ensemble navigates the literal and metaphorical landmines of boot camp, forging unlikely bonds and discovering their true selves in an environment designed to push them to their limits. With sharp wit and plenty of heart, BOOTS is about friendship, resilience, and finding your place in the world—even when that world seems determined to keep you in line or leave you behind.

Netflix is one of the world's leading entertainment services, with over 300 million paid memberships in over 190 countries enjoying TV series, films and games across a wide variety of genres and languages. Members can play, pause and resume watching as much as they want, anytime, anywhere, and can change their plans at any time.

Some doors should never be opened. The Housemaid is the intense new thriller of 2025 starring Sydney Sweeney — secrets, seduction, and danger lurking behind every polished surface.

When a privileged family hires a new maid to help with household chores, they expect nothing but discreet service. What they don’t expect is how quickly she unravels their lives. As intimate secrets emerge, power shifts — and what started as loyalty becomes a game of control, betrayal, and twisted desire.
